
Checkout TVDaemon
==================

git clone https://github.com/neolynx/tvdaemon.git
cd tvdaemon

Build tvdaemon
===============

git submodule init
git submodule update

cd v4l-utils
git checkout master
git am ../patches/*
autoreconf -i
./configure
make
cd -

libtoolize
autoreconf -i
./configure
make

